{"tid":646724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[財雄勢大必贏国] 委內瑞拉欠中國貸款傳屆滿","createTime":"2018-04-29T09:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T16:35:00.000Z","uid":141151,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e4de04cb7861434c01ef315a228770e33c32b949","tid":646724,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T09:53:02.000Z","msg":"委內瑞拉欠中國貸款傳屆滿<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/1831165/%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E6%AC%A0%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E5%82%B3%E5%B1%86%E6%BB%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1831165%2F%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2585%25A7%25E7%2591%259E%25E6%258B%2589%25E6%25AC%25A0%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25B2%25B8%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25B1%2586%25E6%25BB%25BF&d=B4vca9ZrPmCa3H5fW8DSS5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=3ce956ec\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/1831165/%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E6%AC%A0%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E5%82%B3%E5%B1%86%E6%BB%BF</a><br />\n<br />\n路透引述消息人士稱，中國向委內瑞拉提供的借貸寬限期已屆滿，令到該國的財政問題更形嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n中國在2年前向委內瑞拉借貸190億美元，當時是安排了石油換貸款的條款，但委內瑞拉只能夠提供足夠支付利息的石油產品，無力償還本金。消息人士指出，有關貸款寬限期早於數周前結束，儘管委內瑞拉希望中國延長還款期，但雙方談判未有進展。<br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉與委內瑞拉國營石油公司未有回應查詢。"},{"pid":"a292178ee5f3d43dd00346129886d72638f6588f","tid":646724,"uid":12404,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T10:01:44.000Z","msg":"畀人搵笨柒，虫蟈又蠃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8a9e11b42c0be8097b0688fad95c6fb41bcdb9","tid":646724,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T10:02:32.000Z","msg":"對於贏国，幾百億美金都係碎銀者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e07c2b5e85f4e861a74791002cdfb033da2cd2","tid":646724,"uid":76310,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"